Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.66,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:17705,21668}Whenever my feelings were hurt,\NI couldn't see anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.58,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:21668,25588}because I held a lie in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.55,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25588,29551}Time moved faster than I could react,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:34.59,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29551,34597}so I pulled myself away\Nfrom everything, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:40.64,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:34597,40645}I can't stop anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:47.61,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:41062,47610}Accepting everything, I rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.49,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:49571,53491}I'll fly over all of time\Nwhile holding onto your presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.99,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:53491,56995}following the trace of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:03.00,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56995,63001}My world becomes engulfed with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.25,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:65461,69257}A never ending sky,\Nyour never changing eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.96,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:69257,72969}I want to love these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:19.35,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:72969,79350}No matter the distance,\Nor if we are separated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.77,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:79350,82770}we are always connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}Want you here tonight!
Comment: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:91112,91112}Introduction
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:35.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93281,95408}{\i1}Meimi Haneoka is 14 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:38.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95408,98620}{\i1}By day she is a happy student\Nat St. Paulia School.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:42.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99621,102832}{\i1}But at night, she becomes\Nthe phantom thief St. Tail
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:47.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102832,107545}{\i1}to do good deeds for all who come\Nasking for help from Seira, a nun in training.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:51.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:107545,111799}{\i1}Looking to capture the elusive St. Tail\Nis an amateur detective
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:54.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111799,114636}{\i1}and Meimi's classmate, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:59.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114636,119140}{\i1}As for Meimi, she may have more than\Na bit of interest in such a determined boy.
Comment: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:01.14,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:121142,121142}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:05.85,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:122935,125855}I Hate Wedding Veils.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:13.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132195,133196}So what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:14.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133196,134322}Are you going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:17.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135239,137450}Well, I guess I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:20.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137450,140411}Thank you!\NNow that it's decided, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:32.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150463,152465}Oh! It's already full!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:35.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152465,155677}It sure is popular.\NShall we come another day?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:36.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155677,156552}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:41.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156552,161224}I didn't get any last time and today,\NI wanna eat some chocolate chip!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:43.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161224,163267}You're acting very immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:45.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163267,165478}Yeah, just like a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:51.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167689,171234}Your obsession with ice cream\Nproves your lack of maturity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171234,172860}Keep your opinion to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:55.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172860,175321}It's popular with\Ncollege girls, too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:59.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176114,179909}Those college girls\Nare just as immature as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:03.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181703,183621}Just who are "you"\Ncalling immature?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:05.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184080,185039}Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:07.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185039,187125}You're barely out of diapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:09.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187125,189085}Should we teach him\Nhow to have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:13.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189544,193047}Um… I… Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:28.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206728,208354}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209063,210106}Heaven's punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:31.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210648,211941}But still…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:33.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212567,213401}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:34.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213401,214444}It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:35.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214444,215862}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:36.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215862,216904}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220241,222201}I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:44.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223411,224829}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:48.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227498,228624}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:49.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228624,229667}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:53.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232587,233921}See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249061,250563}Oh, welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:12.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251355,252565}I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:16.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253149,256068}What's the matter Meimi?\NYou don't look very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:18.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256068,258905}The happiness of a family\Ncomes from healthy greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:21.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258905,261032}Let's try again!\NWelcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:25.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264285,265912}I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269582,271417}My new trick…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272001,273044}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279634,281552}Looks like she's in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:45.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282970,285515}Maybe she did badly on a test?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:48.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285890,288476}What's that jerk's problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292939,294899}Oh, Ruby, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:58.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295817,298903}I didn't mean to snap at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:03.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300112,303616}Why am I so irritated?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:07.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303616,307370}He's not supposed to\Nmean anything to me and still…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311415,312875}I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313709,316546}I don't even know\Nwhy I feel this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:18.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317129,318840}How annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330226,332311}Dear God.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:37.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332311,337233}Please grant my wish.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:38.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337567,338734}I'm so glad…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338734,340194}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:42.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340194,342029}Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:47.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343030,347660}Oh, how beautiful!\NIt's a wedding veil, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349579,351289}It's really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:53.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351914,353499}Papa, why is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353499,354625}Who is it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:57.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355167,357128}Does it make you happy, Sayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:00.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358337,360631}The wedding veil is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360631,362842}For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362842,364927}It's a gift from your fiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366888,368764}Isn't it wonderful, Sayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368764,370057}Yes, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:23.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381110,383487}Meimi, Seira, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383487,384363}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:25.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384363,385448}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:28.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385448,388075}What's the matter Meimi?\NYou don't look too happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388618,390453}Maybe she's found\Nthat special someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393039,394957}Who is it? Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395541,397752}Today is an important day,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397752,400630}but you haven't prepared\Nfor it at all, am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:42.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401339,402590}That's right…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:45.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402882,405676}Oh no! I haven't prepared either!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:48.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405676,408471}I'm sure you're well prepared,\Naren't you, Seira?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408471,410056}Tell me, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:53.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410556,413017}Studying is something\None must do on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:55.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413351,415019}That's harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:57.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415019,417021}That's just how she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417855,419732}You've got ten minutes\Nuntil class starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420107,421400}Excuse us…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422026,423194}Seniors…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:05.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423569,425863}They're the badminton\Nclub freshmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425863,427490}Aren't they cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427490,429158}Oh… that girl is…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429659,431118}That's Sayaka Shinomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:13.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431118,433120}She's cute and really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:16.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433120,436374}I hear she lives in an\Nold mansion at the edge of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:25.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441671,445883}Hey, I wonder what\Nshe's staring at so intensely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:30.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445883,450054}You're right.\NShe's staring pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:53.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469198,473953}So the wedding veil is a\Ntoken of your engagement?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:58.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474412,478958}Yes, but…\NI've never even met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:05.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481919,485297}My parents arranged\Nthe engagement themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486841,488259}You poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:11.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489677,491429}On top of that, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:14.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492304,494056}There's someone else\NI'm in love with!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:22.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501313,502606}Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:26.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502606,506819}I don't want to be engaged\Nto a stranger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:31.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507361,511032}If only that veil would disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513743,514952}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:38.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514952,518497}Please give me the strength\Nto dissolve this engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:42.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519832,522960}May the blessings\Nof God be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:53.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529467,533179}And there's nothing\NSayaka can do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533179,535264}It seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:09:01.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535264,541145}All right! St. Tail shall steal\Nthat wedding veil!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:06.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541645,546609}Even if the person Sayaka\Nis in love with is Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:12.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548611,552156}Gross! What terrible taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552907,554950}What are you going to do Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:17.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554950,557411}Why are you asking\Nme something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:18.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557411,558537}Then you don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:23.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559371,563292}Of course not!\NSt. Tail never has second thoughts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:26.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563292,566420}I'll steal that wedding veil,\Nno matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567963,569965}Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:37.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571842,577890}So you see, they completely\Ndisregarded a young girl's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:42.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579141,582061}It's unforgivable.\NIsn't that right, Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:09.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605376,609630}"Tonight, I'm going to steal a wedding veil\Nfrom the Shinomiya residence."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610131,611423}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:15.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613217,615636}What's all that noise\Nthis early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616137,618430}It's a vocal warm up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:22.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618430,622059}Forget it.\NMusic doesn't run in our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622059,623018}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:28.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625563,628983}I know I told her to\Nkeep me informed, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:36.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635197,636657}I guess I won't wash my face.
Comment: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:36.65,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:636657,636657}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:42.66,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:642663,642663}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:47.66,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:647668,647668}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:58.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655551,658387}Hey, what are you doing?\NHurry up and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:02.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659471,662474}Look, I made a really good\Nsunny-side-up egg today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662474,664059}I don't want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:06.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664852,666103}What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:10.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666103,670024}When you make them, you grumble\Nif anything is left on the plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:12.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670816,672026}I don't want to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:15.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672943,675154}A growing boy like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:18.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675154,678532}If I eat, the note might disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:20.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678532,680409}I've just got some stuff going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680409,682578}What, you found yourself\Na girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:23.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682578,683996}Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:30.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684955,690461}Why do you keep your back turned?\NWhen you talk to somebody, face them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:35.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691712,695424}I've got stuff going on so… see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:40.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698385,700387}Is that really St. Tail's note?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:42.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700763,702097}That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:43.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702097,703098}Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:46.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703098,706644}But you're a real idiot, having slept\Nthrough her writing it on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706644,708020}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:49.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708020,709897}Let me touch it real quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709897,711690}Stupid! Don't touch it!\NYour hands are dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:52.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711690,712942}How silly…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:53.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712942,713817}Hey, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:58.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713817,718781}Cut it out, you idiot! Knock it off!\NShe's mine! I'm gonna get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:00.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719531,720908}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:03.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722159,723118}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:08.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724787,728874}Even if the person Sayaka\Nis in love with is Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:17.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736757,737633}Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:22.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741011,742304}Asuka…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:24.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743055,744139}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:32.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748394,752606}…therefore I'd appreciate\Nyou letting me stake the place out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753524,754525}Uhm…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754525,756068}Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757152,758821}There's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:45.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758821,765494}St. Tail has never gone back\Non a warning or failed in a caper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:48.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765494,768038}If you take her lightly,\Nyou'll be in a terrible situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:54.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771292,774169}Let's go over the\Nplan for this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:57.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774169,777256}On top of getting the veil stolen,\NI can win over Asuka Jr., too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:13:00.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777256,780467}If this is the case, I wish\NMiss Thief could come every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:08.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784638,788392}Well, time to work.\NGotta help those in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801322,802323}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802990,804908}I thought I heard\Nsomething in the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:28.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806952,808370}I think someone's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:32.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809163,812333}In situations like this\Nit's usually a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:36.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814168,816337}Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816920,818589}You're right. Just a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820883,822593}{\i1}She's my daughter, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:07.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843655,847159}Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:13.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852289,853165}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:16.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855501,856835}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:19.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858837,859880}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:40.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876313,880109}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:42.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880859,882236}Well, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:44.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882236,884363}Are you really going Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:45.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884363,885072}I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:50.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885614,890035}If I were Sayaka, I wouldn't want\Nan engagement like that, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:56.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:892037,896792}If the veil is returned, I'm sure\Nthe engagement will be called off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:59.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897459,899753}Can you do it, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:03.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900379,903215}Without a doubt, if it's God's will!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:09.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904383,909012}This "Tail" thief is probably thinking\Nof entering through the attic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:16.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911640,916437}So I'm going to stand watch in the room\Ndirectly below the attic, for an ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:20.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917771,920399}But, what if she enters\Nfrom a different place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:23.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921275,923277}If I say she's coming through here,\Nthat's how it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:28.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923819,928365}I've met up with her many times\Nand I know what to expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:32.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:929158,932327}Are you absolutely sure it's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:37.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934913,937791}Papa, don't be rude to Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:43.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938917,943297}Papa, Mama, will you wait outside?\NAsuka and I will keep watch here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944673,946341}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946341,947968}Well, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:52.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:947968,952222}I'm sure you'll be able to catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:55.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952931,955184}What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956351,958145}Okay, just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:03.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961440,963609}There's something odd…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:08.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964860,968197}St. Tail never steals\Nwithout a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:13.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969364,973243}Why would she want\Nto steal a wedding veil?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973243,974369}Well that's…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:15.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974369,975579}Mr. Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:17.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975996,977122}The inner courtyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984963,986590}Hurry and do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:31.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987341,991178}Even if she uses a decoy\Nor some sort of camouflage…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:36.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994765,996308}There's nothing to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:39.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996642,999186}I'm not such a dimwit that I'd be\Ncaught with the same trick twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:46.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003023,1006610}He's not falling for my tricks.\NHow boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:50.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006610,1010697}Well, if he's looking for a challenge,\NI'll give him one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:03.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018789,1023585}The security is pretty bad.\NNo guards or anything so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:14.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031134,1034972}The wedding veil and\NAsuka Jr. are waiting just for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034972,1036765}One small setback.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:20.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036765,1040477}But, with the veil right in front of me,\NI can't back down now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:27.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045857,1047693}St. Tail! You've taken the bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:39.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058036,1059788}Applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:42.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060038,1062708}Applause, my foot!\NThat's no fair! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:46.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064418,1066253}Let me go! She's going to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:47.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066253,1067754}But I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067754,1069214}Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:51.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069214,1071508}Miss Thief, take it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:54.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071842,1074011}Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:58.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076930,1078807}She's gonna escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:00.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078807,1080267}I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:07.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082686,1087232}Stealing this veil means Sayaka's\Nengagement will be called off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:10.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088150,1090193}It's the right thing to do, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:16.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094031,1096033}She's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102539,1104041}I'm gonna catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:35.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114259,1115469}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:42.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116511,1122434}Wait! Answer me one question!\NWhy are you stealing that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:46.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123560,1126855}Are you just a thief, after all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:52.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129149,1132361}Haven't you always stolen\Nto help those in trouble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:57.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135781,1137240}How about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:19:01.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137240,1141078}How about you? Why don't you\Never understand how a girl feels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:07.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142496,1147042}If you want to know who\Nthe troubled one is, ask Sayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:10.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147793,1150045}You super-dingbat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:15.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153757,1155842}Ding… bat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161890,1163767}She got away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:31.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168105,1171358}I won't give up!\NI'll never give in to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:34.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172776,1174945}Darn it!
